parameters.query:
SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';

SELECT A.* 
FROM (
    SELECT DISTINCT
        b.ref_no, 
        b.status,
        b.reason,
        CASE 
            WHEN (b.reason IN ('Car is not available - under maintenance','I change my mind regarding my carâ€™s availability') OR b.reason ~* '(workshop)') THEN 'Availability' 
            WHEN b.reason ~* '(delivery)' THEN 'Delivery'
            WHEN b.reason ~* '(contact)' THEN 'Contact'
            WHEN b.reason = 'auto-rejected' AND (EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (b.request_start_at - b.created_at)) / 3600) >= 8 AND ((EXTRACT(HOUR FROM b.created_at)) <= 23 OR (EXTRACT(HOUR FROM b.created_at)) >= 6) THEN 'Auto_rejected'
            WHEN (b.reason = 'auto-rejected-incompleted-profile' OR (b.reason = 'auto-rejected' AND (EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (b.request_start_at - b.created_at)) / 3600) < 8 AND ((EXTRACT(HOUR FROM b.created_at)) >= 23 OR (EXTRACT(HOUR FROM b.created_at)) <= 6))) THEN 'Exclude'
            ELSE 'Others'
        END AS rej_type,
        b.created_at::timestamp, 
        b.updated_at::timestamp, 
        b.request_start_at::timestamp, 
        b.request_end_at::timestamp,
        b.user_id AS guest_id, 
        CONCAT(u2.first_name,' ',u2.last_name) AS guest_name,
        l.id, 
        l.registration_no, 
        l.user_id,
        CONCAT(u.first_name,' ',u.last_name) AS host_name,
        u.email, 
        u.uuid, 
        m.name AS model
    FROM 
        bookings b 
        LEFT JOIN listings l ON l.id = b.listing_id
        LEFT JOIN users u ON u.id = l.user_id
        LEFT JOIN users u2 ON u2.id = b.user_id 
        LEFT JOIN models m ON m.id = l.model_id 
        LEFT JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT listing_id, country, city_id FROM listing_location) ll ON ll.listing_id = b.listing_id
    WHERE 
        1=1
        AND b.status = 'rejected'
        AND ll.country = 'Malaysia'
        AND b.updated_at::timestamp >= (NOW() - INTERVAL '1 days')
        -- AND b.listing_id = '20035'
) A;
-- WHERE A.rej_type = 'Delivery'
-- LIMIT 1;
